00:00:10,660 --> 00:00:25,640
Hello everyone, and welcome to episode 5 of the Octothorpe podcast,

5
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:29,600
a podcast about science fiction and SF fandom. I'm Jon Coxon.

6
00:00:30,040 --> 00:00:31,080
I'm Alison Scott.

7
00:00:31,080 --> 00:00:32,360
