10
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:48,120
Alison and Liz, do you want to reveal the secrets behind the curtain?

11
00:00:48,120 --> 00:00:52,560
It's because if we don't go Jon, Alison, Liz, then...

12
00:00:52,560 --> 00:00:55,200
Then Alison and I talk at exactly the same time.

13
00:00:55,200 --> 00:00:58,920
And every time we try and do it again, we again talk exactly the same time

14
00:00:58,920 --> 00:01:01,760
and dissolve in fits of giggles and Jon Franz has.

15
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:05,180
And says we have to do it again.

16
00:01:05,180 --> 00:01:09,540
The beauty of having you record on separate tracks is actually that I can make it sound

17
00:01:09,540 --> 00:01:11,180
like you didn't talk at the same time.

18
00:01:11,180 --> 00:01:14,560
But yes, it does sound weird when you're listening to it live.

19
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:18,360
Yeah, but Claire is very observant and noticed that we do this.

20
00:01:18,360 --> 00:01:19,880
But yes, that is indeed the reason.

21
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:23,180
Claire also gave us some corrections.

22
