So she noted that we got the fan fund bounty stuff slightly wrong last week.

23
00:01:30,140 --> 00:01:34,660
I did put that in the show notes because I realised I had done it wrong while I was talking about it.

24
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:44,000
But she noted that Fanac doesn't cover the guff trip reports and sci-fi still does.

25
