131
00:07:35,580 --> 00:07:36,800
And I drank too much ale.

132
00:07:36,800 --> 00:07:38,760
So it was exactly the same as a real Easter Con,

133
00:07:38,760 --> 00:07:40,300
apart from the fact that I woke up,

134
00:07:40,300 --> 00:07:40,840
you know,

135
00:07:41,340 --> 00:07:44,900
in my own bed at home and didn't have to manage hotels and things.

136
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:47,660
But also nobody cooked me enormous breakfast,

137
00:07:47,660 --> 00:07:48,840
which was a bit of a shame.

138
00:07:48,840 --> 00:07:52,000
I do wonder that for people like me,

139
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:55,180
who habitually don't attend a lot of the programme,

140
00:07:55,180 --> 00:07:56,320
what the,

141
00:07:56,320 --> 00:07:56,580
I mean,

142
00:07:56,680 --> 00:08:00,060
I am Con Zealand accompanying my membership as the Guff delegate

143
00:08:00,060 --> 00:08:01,460
and I am extremely grateful to them.

144
00:08:01,460 --> 00:08:02,380
Thank you very much.

145
00:08:02,380 --> 00:08:03,920
That is very kind of them.

146
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,860
And I will come along and of course I'll be on programme

147
00:08:05,860 --> 00:08:08,320
and I will do programme-y things during the programme time.

148
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:10,200
We're going to talk a bit about Guff later,

