00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:12,180
but for people who aren't me,

150
00:08:12,180 --> 00:08:15,080
but who are kind of party type fans,

151
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:19,720
I do slightly wonder if the primary benefit of a Worldcon for you

152
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:21,260
is the socialisation structure,

153
00:08:21,260 --> 00:08:24,240
what it is that you get for your attending membership.

154
00:08:24,940 --> 00:08:29,220
So they do say that as part of their collaboration with the Fantasy Network

155
00:08:29,220 --> 00:08:31,160
that they're going to try and have some,

156
00:08:31,160 --> 00:08:31,620
you know,

157
00:08:31,620 --> 00:08:33,100
as well as the panels and video,

158
00:08:33,100 --> 00:08:35,900
they will also have like networking and late night hanging out

159
00:08:35,900 --> 00:08:37,840
and informal hangouts as well,

160
00:08:37,840 --> 00:08:39,040
which I think they're right.

161
00:08:39,040 --> 00:08:39,980
That is like a key,

162
00:08:39,980 --> 00:08:41,260
a key part of the Worldcon.

163
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:43,820
