166
00:08:50,540 --> 00:08:53,380
I think I'm quite pleased to see that they've got this partnership going

167
00:08:53,380 --> 00:08:56,400
because it sounds like they've got some people who are really experienced

168
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:58,080
at doing sort of video on demand.

169
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:00,020
And so it will be,

170
00:09:00,020 --> 00:09:01,040
I presume,

171
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:02,460
all quite nicely done.

172
00:09:02,460 --> 00:09:03,420
There won't be a lot of this.

